author: Branch Education
description:
Have you ever wondered how all the hardware inside a computer fits together?  Well in this video we take apart a modern computer and examine all the hardware.  We'll look at things like the CPU, the GPU, the Motherboard, the DRAM, the SSDs, the Hard Disk Drives, the Power Supply, the Water Cooler, and everything else.

For more info: https://youtu.be/d86ws7mQYIg
title: How do Desktop Computers Work? #pcbuild #computerhardware
